'From Squeak3.7alpha of ''11 September 2003'' [latest update: #5657] on 2 February 2004 at 1:51:06 pm'!"Change Set:		KCP-198-BrowserDate:			2 February 2004Author:			stephane ducasseremove one hardecoded reference in Browser"!!Browser class methodsFor: 'instance creation' stamp: 'sd 2/2/2004 13:50'!fullOnClass: aClass 	"Open a new full browser set to class."	| brow |	brow _ self new.	brow setClass: aClass selector: nil.	^ self 		openBrowserView: (brow openEditString: nil)		label: 'System Browser'! !